      },
      "content": "\"Load bearing,\" \"I keep coming back to,\" \"Not just X, but Y\" \n\nA curse of using AI a lot is that you realize how much of the writing around you is just AI, now\n\nPeople who don't use AI have historically been unable to identify AI prose on sight, but those who use it a lot can spot the tells easily",
